subparagraph.text:

Subsections (b) and (c) of section 303 of the Servicemembers Civil Relief Act (
  50 U.S.C. App. 533
), as amended by subsections (a) and (b) of this section, are amended by striking within one year each place it appears and inserting within 90 days.

section.text:

Section 203 of the Servicemembers Civil Relief Act (
  50 U.S.C. App. 523
) is amended by adding at the end the following new subsection:

subsection.text:

Paragraph (2) of such section (
  50 U.S.C. App. 521(b)
) is amended—

subparagraph.text:
references to
				false claims law investigators or investigations shall be considered references
				to investigators or investigations under this Act;

references to
				interrogatories shall be considered references to written questions, and
				answers to such need not be under oath;

the
